Download maven binary file from official website https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi in /opt directory

After downloading, create maven.sh file in /etc/profile.d directory

Edit maven.sh with following content:
export M2_HOME=/opt/apache-maven-3.9.9
eport PATH=${M2_HOME}/bin:${PATH}

Provide full access to maven.sh

Execute the following command to load maven.sh globally
source /etc/profile.d/maven.sh
